sentence: We have acted as counsel for Sonic Automotive, Inc., a Delaware corporation (the Company), and the subsidiaries of the Company named as co-registrants in the Form S-4 (the Guarantors and together with the Company, the Issuers), in connection with the registration by the Company and the Guarantors under the Securities Act of 1933, as amended (the Securities Act), of the offer and issuance of up to $ 210,000,000 aggregate principal amount of the Company s 9.0 % Senior Subordinated Notes due 2018, Series B with guarantees (the Exchange Notes) to be offered by the Issuers in exchange for a like principal amount of the Company s issued and outstanding 9.0 % Senior Subordinated Notes due 2018, Series A (the Original Notes).
